\citation{cuda-dp4a,cublas}
\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Format A vs B trit-budget sweep on Llama 1B. The 15-trit and B 9-trit logits are essentially identical (RMSE 0.004); argmax differs by tie-breaking between two near-equal candidates. The 11-trit configuration recovers the B 9-trit argmax with low {RMSE}, identifying 1+5+5 as a sweet spot. The 7-trit budget breaks both argmax and {RMSE}.}}{4}{table.1}\protected@file@percent }
